Come on! Come on.

01:48:56.714 --> 01:49:01.445
Alright... we'll take up, you
guys flank around from there.

01:49:45.182 --> 01:49:45.965
There he is!

01:49:52.270 --> 01:49:53.636
Nicholas Sloan!

01:49:55.083 --> 01:50:00.900
You're under arrest for the
murder of Hugh Kroessna.

01:50:10.080 --> 01:50:12.180
Can't say I'm happy to see you.

01:51:49.342 --> 01:51:53.450
Mimi Lurie, last remaining fugitive
from the 1980 Bank of Michigan robbery,

01:51:53.550 --> 01:51:56.946
surrendered herself to authorities today
near Drummond Island, Michigan,

01:51:57.047 --> 01:51:58.947
just across the water from Canada.

01:51:59.047 --> 01:52:03.126
She confessed to her role in the robbery,
which resulted in the death of a guard.

01:52:03.427 --> 01:52:05.736
Charges have been dropped
against Nicholas Sloan,

01:52:05.936 --> 01:52:08.856
long thought to be a co-conspirator
in the robbery.

01:52:08.957 --> 01:52:11.693
No comment yet from
Sloan, who is expected to

01:52:11.706 --> 01:52:14.453
be released from custody
as early as tomorrow.

